details.purpose: To ecord details of assisted ventilation parameters.
details.use: May be used both on the context of instructing these parameters to be set and in recording the parameters actualy in use either manually or direct from the device.

details.purpose: To record details of ventilator settings, such as ventilation type, volume, frequencies and pressures.
